---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Books — Verdandi Weaver
description: The library of Verdandi Weaver — books on grounded wholeness, awakening, and being human.
permalink: /books.html
---

<section class="hero container fade-up">
  <p class="t-eyebrow hero__eyebrow">A digital library</p>
  <h1 class="t-h1 hero__title t-balance">Books</h1>
  <p class="t-lead hero__lead t-pretty">Slow reading for the long return — being human, belonging, and the texture of wholeness.</p>
</section>

<section class="section section--sunk fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-3" style="row-gap: var(--sp-8);">
      {% set books = collections.book | sort(false, false, "data.order") %}
      {% for book in books %}
      <article class="book">
        {% if book.data.image %}
        <div class="book__cover book__cover--img"><img src="{{ book.data.image }}" alt="{{ book.data.title }}" /></div>
        {% else %}
        <div class="book__cover book__cover--{{ book.data.cover }}">{{ book.data.title }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        <h3 class="book__title">{{ book.data.title }}</h3>
        <p class="book__meta">{{ book.data.meta }}</p>
        <p class="book__desc">{{ book.data.description }}</p>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section fade-up">
  <div class="container narrow center-text">
    <p class="pull">Each book is a doorway. Pick the one that breathes loudest in you today.</p>
    <p class="t-meta" style="margin-top: var(--sp-5);">Audiobook editions are slowly being prepared.</p>
  </div>
</section>
